column5: came across this ad ....great deal for anyone needing some ice fishing gear  http://london.kijiji.ca/c-buy-and-sell-sporting-goods-exercise-fishing-camping-outdoors-ICE-FISHING-8-AUGER-AND-PORTABLE-HUT-200-FIRM-W0QQAdIdZ408029037
Man, if I lived near there, that'd be mine. Quite the deal.
Dana, I can pick it up & get it to Mississauga for you if you can make arrangements for the rest of the way.
My strike master will be up for sale soon. One tank of fuel through it.Probly around 275. 8 inch.
Thanks for the offer - much appreciated! However, that's still about 5-6 hours away from me, and I don't know anyone there or have any plans to travel anytime soon. Thanks, though!
